WEBVTT

00:04:29.076 --> 00:04:32.580
would be all dome

00:04:32.604 --> 00:04:36.075
and everything we kept making
was looking too much like an egg.

00:04:36.099 --> 00:04:37.709
(Laughter)

00:04:37.733 --> 00:04:38.956
A blob.

00:04:39.706 --> 00:04:40.924
So you search.

00:04:41.529 --> 00:04:46.032
You all know this crazy search,
letting the process take you,

00:04:46.056 --> 00:04:47.680
and you live for the surprises.

00:04:47.704 --> 00:04:49.930
And I remember quite by accident

00:04:49.954 --> 00:04:55.326
I saw this little video
of a plant moving in light,

00:04:55.350 --> 00:04:59.013
and it made me think of movement,

00:04:59.037 --> 00:05:00.209
reach,